等合作。\n70后的泽连斯基，将会给年迈的欧洲带来活力和希望\n\n---\n\n标题：Stanford University\nURL：https://www.usnews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-humanities-schools/stanford-university-243744\n站点名称：U.S. News & World Report\n发布时间：\n摘要：\nFind out at US News. See if Stanford University is ra...\n\n---\n\n标题：stanford\nURL：https://bulletin.stanford.edu/\n站点名称：Stanford University Bulletin\n发布时间：\n摘要：\nWith more than 7,000 undergraduates and 9,000 graduates studying across our seven schools on our one campus, Stanford’s abundant offerings provide our ...', 'id': 'lc_125db082-d6db-4aa3-889e-a080974010c2'}], name='common_search', id='d8defde4-9cec-4be9-96d2-e36d7a0df0a7', tool_call_id='call_324c2fb4dc734d7596674c99'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 115, 'prompt_tokens': 6293, 'total_tokens': 6408, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 115}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': None, 'cached_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 6293}}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'qwen3.5-plus', 'system_fingerprint': None, 'id': 'chatcmpl-62e99894-9844-9acf-ae30-d6396835091a', 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'logprobs': None}, name='researcher', id='lc_run--019c9e0d-9c00-7961-b3ee-29c3745abd26-0', tool_calls=[{'name': 'crawl_tool', 'args': {'__arg1': 'https://bkso.baidu.com/item/%E4%B9%8C%E5%B0%94%E8%8B%8F%E6%8B%89%C2%B7%E5%86%AF%E5%BE%B7%E8%8E%B1%E6%81%A9/12700646?fromModule=lemma_inlink'}, 'id': 'call_9ec13b2fc1894c0aaa6f8c2a', 'type': 'tool_call'}], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 6293, 'output_tokens': 115, 'total_tokens': 6408, 'input_token_details': {}, 'output_token_details': {'reasoning': 0}}), ToolMessage(content="Error scraping https://bkso.baidu.com/item/%E4%B9%8C%E5%B0%94%E8%8B%8F%E6%8B%89%C2%B7%E5%86%AF%E5%BE%B7%E8%8E%B1%E6%81%A9/12700646?fromModule=lemma_inlink: HTTPSC