soning': 0}}), ToolMessage(content='Link: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borussia_Dortmund_Youth_Sector\n\nPage: Borussia Dortmund Youth Sector\nSummary: Borussia Dortmund Youth Sector is the youth set-up of Borussia Dortmund. The club operates the system for boys from the age of nine upwards and a total of 15 youth teams. Home games are staged at the club\'s training ground Hohenbuschei.\nLars Ricken, a former Dortmund player and German international, has been the youth coordinator since 2008.\nThe youth team has educated many players who have become regulars in the Bundesliga and the Germany national football team, such as Eike Immel, Lars Ricken and the current club Director for Sport Michael Zorc. Most recent graduates include first team regulars Marco Reus, Nuri Şahin and Marcel Schmelzer. The club has notably produced World Cup champions Mario Götze and Kevin Großkreutz.\n\nPage: 2017 DFB-Pokal final\nSummary: The 2017 DFB-Pokal final decided the winner of the 2016–17 DFB-Pokal, the 74th season of the annual German football cup competition. The match was played on 27 May 2017 at the Olympiastadion in Berlin.\nEintracht Frankfurt, in their first final since 2006, faced Borussia Dortmund, the runners-up in the previous three finals. Borussia Dortmund won the match 2–1 to claim their fourth cup title.\nAs winners, Borussia Dortmund hosted the 2017 edition of the DFL-Supercup at the start of the next season, and faced the champions of the 2016–17 edition of the Bundesliga, Bayern Munich. The winners of the DFB-Pokal were also to earn automatic qualification for the group stage of the 2017–18 edition of the UEFA Europa League, but since Borussia Dortmund had already qualified for the 2017–18 edition of the UEFA Champions League through their position in the Bundesliga, the group stage spot went to the team in sixth, Hertha BSC, and the league\'s third qualifying round spot to the team in seventh, SC Freiburg.\n\nPage: Thomas Stamm\nSummary: Thomas Stamm (born 19 February 1983) is a Swiss football manager and former player who is the head coach of 2. Bundesliga club Dynamo Dresden.\n\n--- [Automatic Crawl of Top Result: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borussia_Dortmund_Youth_Sector] ---\nTitle: Borussia Dortmund Youth Sector\n\nURL Source: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borussia_Dortmund_Youth_Sector\n\nPublished Time: 2011-07-19T19:49:16Z\n\nMarkdown Content:\nFrom Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia\n\nBorussia Dortmund Youth Sector[![Image 1: crest](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/67/Borussia_Dortmund_logo.svg/250px-Borussia_Dortmund_logo.svg.png)](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Borussia_Dortmund_logo.svg "crest")\nFull name Ballspielverein Borussia\n\n09 e.V. Dortmund\nPresident Dr [Reinhard Rauball](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reinhard_Rauball "Reinhard Rauball")\nYouth Coordinator[Thomas Broich](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Broich "Thomas Broich")\nWebsite[www.bvb.de](http://www.bvb.de/)\n\n![Image 2](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2d/Kit_left_arm_bvb2122H.png) ![Image 3](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Kit_left_arm.svg/40px-Kit_left_arm.svg.png) ![Image 4](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2a/Kit_body_bvb2122H.png) ![Image 5](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/83/Kit_body.svg/40px-Kit_body.svg.png) ![Image 6](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8e/Kit_right_arm_bvb2122H.png) ![Image 7](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cd/Kit_right_arm.svg/40px-Kit_right_arm.svg.png) ![Image 8](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Kit_shorts.svg/120px-Kit_shorts.svg.png) ![Image 9](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/c... [truncated]', name='wikipedia', id='838cd596-2884-426b-8548-bb54b17c6cfe', tool_call_id='call_201035d57f1e4573899d5cec'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 59, 'prompt_tokens': 23207, 'total_tokens': 23266, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 59}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': None, 'cached_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 23207}}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'qwen3.5-plus', 'system_fingerprint': None, 'id': 'chatcmpl-4a8e0b7b-bd62-9e68-9ad8-ab8ccf8e3b73', 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'logprobs': None}, name='researcher', id='lc_run--019c9e10-767a-7a51-a317-dff99c6d3915-0', tool_calls=[{'name': 'common_search', 'args': {'query': '斯图加特踢球者 青年队 德国青年杯冠军 1990年代 VfB Stuttgart youth cup 1990s'}, 'id': 'call_b772109e24b1438bb034bcf6', 'type': 'tool_call'}], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 23207, 'output_tokens': 59, 'total_tokens': 23266, 'input_token_details': {}, 'output_token_details': {'reasoning': 0}}), ToolMessage(content="SYSTEM ALERT: You have used the tool 'common_search' 3 times, which is the limit for a single tool. You MUST switch to a DIFFERENT search tool (e.g., use 'academic_search' or 'web_search' instead of 'common_search'). Using the same tool repeatedly is ineffective. TRY ANOTHER TOOL.", name='common_search', id='3a44bc0f-0284-4c1b-b910-82db0092019e', tool_call_id='call_b772109e24b1438bb034bcf6'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 52, 'prompt_tokens': 23348, 'total_tokens': 23400, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': None, 'audio_tokens': None, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 52}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': None, 'cached_tokens': None, 'text_tokens': 23348}}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'qwen3.5-plus', 'system_fingerprint': None, 'id': 'chatcmpl-00d87e02-17de-909f-afd0-f8141ff646ed', 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'logprobs': None}, name='researcher', id='lc_run--019c9e10-85d5-7343-